{"type":"article","id":5728,"title":"韩国瑜祭孔，穿的是满洲衣冠","uid":8354,"topics":[805,676,316,1,163,16],"contents":"<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EFpItL_UwAAv1i3?format=png&amp;name=900x900\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EFpItL_UwAAv1i3?format=png&amp;name=900x900\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EFpItL_UwAAv1i3?format=png&amp;name=900x900\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>中国人韩国瑜祭孔，穿的是满洲衣冠，其实他的祭文也不妨改用满洲语。因为大多数满洲语母语者住在海峡对岸，韩书记用满洲语祭孔，将更加表明他不会亲台卖中。而且四书五经都有可汗钦定的满文版，满洲语祭文不难写的。<br>\n<br>\n顺便把我翻译的满文“愿荣光归香港”最后一段贴出来：<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EEX9mdrWsAAUCLa?format=png&amp;name=900x900\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EEX9mdrWsAAUCLa?format=png&amp;name=900x900\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EEX9mdrWsAAUCLa?format=png&amp;name=900x900\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-09-29","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}